These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, punk, reggae, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, american, argentine, polish
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, goat, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, motorbike, car
 1. the pakistani is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the american##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 6. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 7. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the american##5
 9. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the argentine##3
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the fan of metal##7
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
12. the polish is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
13. the person driving the car is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | punk | reggae    | metal   |
| Nationality   | pakistani | argentine | american | polish |
| Pet           | fish       | goat   | guinea-pig  | ferret     |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | motorbike   | car    | bus    |

