.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cherry, lettuce, broccoli
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, sports, musical, action
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, russian, thai, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, swimming, biathlon, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
 2. the thai is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the canadian##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the thai##3
 6. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
 7. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the canadian##7
 8. the person eating plum is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
10. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##5
11. the russian is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | plum   | lettuce       | broccoli    | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | action | sports         | musical   |
| Nationality   | american   | canadian  | russian       | thai |
| Sport         | surfing      | biathlon  | rowing | swimming |

