.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, lawyer, entrepreneur, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, thriller, time-travel, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, turkish, canadian
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, chinchilla, pony
 1. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 2. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the paramedic and the person watching time-travel movies##7
 3. the lawyer is the american##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the musician##3
 5. the mexican is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
 7. the entrepreneur is not the person watching thriller movies##6
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is not the musician##6
 9. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
10. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
11. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
12. the turkish is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | musician | paramedic | lawyer | entrepreneur |
| Movie-Genre   | animation        | satire    | thriller    | time-travel    |
| Nationality   | mexican        | canadian   | american   | turkish         |
| Pet           | ferret          | goldfish       | pony   | chinchilla           |

