 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 6. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the designer##1
 8. the musician is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is singing##7
 9. the musician is the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the videographer is not the person watching fantasy movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
