There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cherry, garlic, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, cooking, writing
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, ferret, guinea-pig
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the ferret##2
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 5. the person eating cherry is not the owner of the snake##6
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
 7. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person eating onion##7
 8. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
10. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person drinking water is the person eating garlic##1
12. the person eating garlic is not the owner of the ferret##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | sprite     | hot-chocolate   | water |
| Food       | onion   | cabbage | cherry | garlic    |
| Hobby      | cooking | writing | chess   | sudoku  |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | hedgehog     | ferret   | snake |

