.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, coffee, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, collecting, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, electrician, coach, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, country, trance, pop
 1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 2. the fan of r&b is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the fisherman##2
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 5. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of country is not the coach##6
 7. the coach is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
 8. the fan of r&b is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 9. the freelancer is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
10. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of pop##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person drinking juice##6
13. the coach is on the left of the freelancer##1
14. the fisherman is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
15. the electrician is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice      | iced-tea        | hot-chocolate          | coffee    |
| Hobby         | photography | dancing    | collecting          | card-games |
| Job           | fisherman  | electrician   | coach | freelancer      |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | r&b | trance          | country        |

