.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, gardening, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, dancer, coach
4 different pets are kept: goat, dog, turtle, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, skateboarding, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 2. the dancer is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is the owner of the cat##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 5. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 6. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the dancer and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
 8. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
10. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
12. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | gardening     | puzzles   | collecting    |
| Job     | coach | dancer   | dressmaker | designer |
| Pet     | cat        | turtle     | goat  | dog      |
| Sport   | parkour       | badminton | volleyball   | skateboarding    |

 